commit.message:
* config/darwin.h, config/elfos.h, config/i960/i960-coff.h
	* config/m68k/coff.h: ASM_FILE_START_FILE_DIRECTIVE should
	be TARGET_ASM_FILE_START_FILE_DIRECTIVE.

From-SVN: r68578
